Iavan Pijoos, News24iStock Multimedia &nbsp; &nbsp; User Galleries &nbsp; &nbsp; News in Pictures Send us your pictures &nbsp; &nbsp; Send us your stories Johannesburg - A 37-year-old man from Nigeria&nbsp;has been found murdered in an apartment in Linden, Randburg, police said on Wednesday. Captain Kay Makhubela said the man had a gunshot wound to his upper body.&nbsp; "He was sitting in a chair with a plastic bag over his head. A 9mm cartridge was also found in the living room," Makhubela said.&nbsp; His body was found early on Wednesday morning.&nbsp; The motive for the murder was not yet known.&nbsp; No arrest has been made. &nbsp;24.com encourages commentary submitted via MyNews24. Contributions of 200 words or more will be considered for publication.